          <article about="/content/homepage" class="node node--type-page node--view-mode-full" data-history-node-id="1" role="article" typeof="schema:WebPage">
           <span class="hidden" content="Homepage" property="schema:name">
           </span>
           <div class="node__content">
            <div property="schema:text">
             <h1>
              Harvard Medical School Continuing Medical Education
             </h1>
             <p>
              We greatly appreciate your interest in accrediting your educational activity with Harvard Medical School and look forward to working with you in the design and delivery of an activity to address the diverse learning needs of medical professionals around the globe.
             </p>
             <p>
              Harvard Medical School Continuing Medical Education (HMS CME) is proud to offer an array of course formats. We offer accreditation for the following types of educational activities:
             </p>
             <ul>
              <li>
               Live Activities
              </li>
              <li>
               CME Online Activities
              </li>
              <li>
               Community Activities
              </li>
              <li>
               Regularly Scheduled Series (Grand Rounds, Case Conferences, etc)
              </li>
              <li>
               Live Streamed Activities
              </li>
             </ul>
             <p>
              Our courses are designed to be informative, collaborative, and participatory opportunities for learners to meet our world-class faculty and an engaged community of colleagues. Our professional staff are available to assist with questions and support throughout your course planning process.
             </p>
             <p>
              <img alt="ACCME Accredtation with Commendation" class="align-left" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="41dc9386-b943-4e5c-8a2c-4724eaf218f1" height="130" src="/sites/default/files/img/accme_commendation_cropped.png" width="152"/>
              Harvard Medical School is accredited by the Accreditation Council for Continuing Medical Education (ACCME) to provide continuing medical education for physicians. Harvard Medical School was awarded ACCME's highest level of accreditation, Accreditation with Commendation.
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </article>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
